{"tid":1661002,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣] 文宣圖片可唔可以加入多d少數族裔既參與者？","createTime":"2019-10-18T00:41:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T00:57:10.000Z","uid":293282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cbe4ad07603dbc09e132d1bee5bb76229a3584dc","tid":1661002,"uid":293282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T00:41:30.000Z","msg":"其實抗爭者唔只係華裔香港人，唔少手足其實都係少數族裔。而connect埋少數族裔非常重要，我地亦唔應該忘記佢地。由其是我地如果要獲得更多既國際支持，運動方向就應該要向呢個方向發展。<br />\n<br />\n國際文宣上，不同膚色既參與者對抗港共，其實標榜既就係自由世界vs.威權。我地被提名諾貝爾和平獎，又被加泰抗爭者/環保抗爭者視為學習對象，成功輸出革命，靠既就係呢個方向呢種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n我地要獲得更多既國際支持，呢個係一個重要既方向！"},{"pid":"3835f31a5ceb5e378f2d63363b2d9e18e4366772","tid":1661002,"uid":21548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T00:42:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1ab9701da2aacd8f4e36b82242414ad1ab6d842","tid":1661002,"uid":165244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T00:43:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://previews.123rf.com/images/krissikunterbunt/krissikunterbunt1903/krissikunterbunt190300315/119439245-children-of-different-skin-color-hold-each-other-s-hands-isolated-on-white-background-vector-illustr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpreviews.123rf.com%2Fimages%2Fkrissikunterbunt%2Fkrissikunterbunt1903%2Fkrissikunterbunt190300315%2F119439245-children-of-different-skin-color-hold-each-other-s-hands-isolated-on-white-background-vector-illustr.jpg&h=28f4a169&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd305c29e58d1f5b44d81ccbb2a765fc735c8b0a","tid":1661002,"uid":268213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T00:47:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dde243179b2981a6cf8c0b67b8a785dfce38d721","tid":1661002,"uid":314682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T00:57:10.000Z","msg":"push"}]}